46:18.192 --> 46:19.777
-Really, dude?
-[Fei snickers]

46:19.860 --> 46:22.488
I'm Number One.
You'll do as I say when I say it.

46:22.571 --> 46:23.530
Not anymore.

46:24.990 --> 46:26.909
Here's to a new life
without this dickhead.

